title: Tokyo 8th Edition August 2010
description:
Tokyo city guide
Lonely Planet Travel guide Andrew Bender, Timothy N. Hornyak Aug 2010

Tokyo's permanently set to stun! Where Zen temples nestle in sci-fi cityscapes and centuries-old madness for cherry blossoms coexists with an insatiable desire for nonstop novelty.'Remarkably comprehensive' - The New York Times
Handy pull-out map 
Expanded neighbourhood coverage includes up-and-coming Roppongi Triangle 
Special full-colour Tokyo Pop chapter features everything from anime and robots to high-tech design.
